{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L993"},"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation’s callout view.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotation:calloutaccessorycontroltapped:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNMapView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"mapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"annotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UIControl","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)UIControl"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"control"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"mapView","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The map view containing the specified annotation."}]}]},{"name":"annotation","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation whose accessory view was tapped."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"control","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The control that was tapped."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In a standard callout view, accessory views contain custom content and are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"positioned on either side of the annotation title text. If an accessory view","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"you specify is a descendant of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" class, the map view calls this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method as a convenience whenever the user taps your view. You can use this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method to respond to taps and perform any actions associated with that control.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"For example, if your control displays additional information about the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation, you could use this method to present a modal panel with that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If your custom accessory views are not descendants of the ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIControl","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" class,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the map view does not call this method. If the annotation has a custom callout","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view via the ","type":"text"},{"code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" method, you can specify the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"custom accessory views using the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"leftAccessoryView"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rightAccessoryView"},{"text":" properties.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Related-examples","level":4,"type":"heading","text":"Related examples"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to trigger an action when the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"standard callout bubble’s accessory control is tapped.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation’s callout view."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotation:calloutaccessorycontroltapped:","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNCalloutView":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNCalloutView","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNCalloutView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A protocol for a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" subclass that displays information about a selected"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation near that annotation."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncalloutview"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"require the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","type":"reference"},{"text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"individual annotations.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNMapView"}}}